section.anatomy
	h3 Anatomy of a full-featured text field
	p (w/tooltip, disclosure, and error message containers)

	p Ideal structure without flexbox:

	div.code_sample
		div.field_container
			div.label_container
				label(for="input") label
				button.tooltip info
			div.input_container
				input(
					id="input"
					type="text"
					name="text"
					aria-describedby="disclosure"
					placeholder="input"
					)
				button.button_extra_feature button
			div.error_message#error_message div.error_message
			div.disclosure#disclosure div.disclosure